Hello!

Audience: young entrepreneurs how what to open a new restaurant in the Moscow city center

Business problem: should they open a restaurant? 
If yes, what cuisine the restaurant should have and where the restaurant should be located in the Moscow city center? 


Analytics needed to answer the business problem: 
-	Identification of cuisines with least presence in Moscow city center (the long list of potential cuisines)
-	Selection of areas which are have many restaurants and have at least one cuisine, which are from the previous point, not presented in area
-	Selection of the best cuisine and area for opening
o	Biggest area – more than 50 restaurants
o	Minimum number of cuisines in the Moscow city denter
-	If there is one – then go
